{"title_page": "Ali Nasir", "text_new": "{{for|the Pakistani cricketer|Ali Nasir (cricketer)}}\n{{Use Pakistani English|date=July 2013}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2013}}\n\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Ali Nasir\n| image = Ali Nasir.JPG\n| caption = \n| birthname = \n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1978|10|7}}\n| birth_place = [[Sialkot, Pakistan]]\n| death_date =\n| death_place =\n| occupation = Economist<br>Entrepreneur<br>TV anchor<br>Journalist\n| years_active = 2009\u2013present\n| title =\n| family =\n| spouse =\n| children =\n| relatives =\n| salary = \n| networth =\n| credits = [[Business Plus (TV Channel)|Business Plus]]'s ''Live Wire Insight'' anchor<br> ''Morning Shout'' co-anchor<br>[[Waqt News]] ''The Right Question'' anchor <br> [[Indus TV]]'s ''Talking Business'' anchor\n<br> [[Indus Vision]]'s \"Studio 3\"<ref>{{cite web|last=Ghumman|first=Arsalan|title=PTI Official Page|url=http://www.insaf.pk/Media/Videos/tabid/62/articleType/ArticleView/articleId/15361/Studio3-Arsalan-Ghumman-on-Youth-and-comming-elections-March-12-2013.aspx|publisher=PTI|accessdate=17 March 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316075207/http://www.insaf.pk/Media/Videos/tabid/62/articleType/ArticleView/articleId/15361/Studio3-Arsalan-Ghumman-on-Youth-and-comming-elections-March-12-2013.aspx|archive-date=16 March 2013|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref> \n<br> [[PTV News]]  \"Bulls and Bears\" Occasionally for the market segment\n| URL = http://investorguide360.com/investor-guide-pakistan/\n| agent = \n}}\n'''Ali Nasir''' (born 7 October 1978) is a [[News presenter|news anchor]], media person, broadcast journalist and [[economist]] from [[Pakistan]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Khurshid|first=Ahmed|title=Political instability discourages investment in Pakistan|url=http://www.weeklypulse.org/details.aspx?contentID=1788&storylist|access-date=2 February 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221121030/http://www.weeklypulse.org/details.aspx?contentID=1788&storylist|archive-date=21 February 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Competition Commission of Pakistan interview|url=http://www.cc.gov.pk/index.php/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=29&Itemid=87|publisher=Competition Commission of Pakistan}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Personal Finance and Business Magazine-About-Profile of Key persons|url=http://investorguide360.com/investor-guide-pakistan/|publisher=Investor Guide 360|accessdate=1 November 2012}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://alinasir.weebly.com|title = Ali Nasir - Broadcast Journalist, Economist, Analyst, Historian and researcher|website = Ali Nasir - Broadcast Journalist, Economist, Analyst, Historian and researcher|access-date = 2016-04-13}}</ref>  He regularly appears on [[Geo News]], [[Dawn News]],<ref>{{cite web|last=Zem TV|title=Infocus DAWN Tv 26th January|url=http://www.dailymotion.com/video/x1acgzh_infocus-26th-january-2014_news|publisher=zemtv110|accessdate=7 February 2014}}</ref> [[Business Plus (TV Channel)|Business Plus]], [[SAMAA TV]], [[AAJ TV]], [[Metro One]], [[News One]], [[Din News]], [[Waqt News]], Royal News, and [[Indus News]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Ali Nasir Economist YouTube Channel|url=https://www.youtube.com/user/MrAnasir7?feature=mhee|publisher=YouTube}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Kya Hum Tayar Hain-2nd June 2012|url=http://www.awaztoday.co/News-Talk-Shows/23785/Kya-Hum-Tayyar-Hain-2nd-June-2012.aspx|publisher=Awaz.tv|accessdate=1 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221105359/http://www.awaztoday.co/News-Talk-Shows/23785/Kya-Hum-Tayyar-Hain-2nd-June-2012.aspx|archive-date=21 February 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Kya Hum Tayar Hain|url=http://www.awaztoday.co/News-Talk-Shows/24786/Kya-Hum-Tayar-Hain-30th-June-2012.aspx|publisher=Awaz.tv|access-date=1 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221104946/http://www.awaztoday.co/News-Talk-Shows/24786/Kya-Hum-Tayar-Hain-30th-June-2012.aspx|archive-date=21 February 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Kya Hum Tayar Hain 30 sept 2012|url=http://www.awaztoday.co/News-Talk-Shows/27220/Kya-Hum-Tayar-Hain-8th-September-2012.aspx|publisher=Awaz.tv|access-date=1 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221112132/http://www.awaztoday.co/News-Talk-Shows/27220/Kya-Hum-Tayar-Hain-8th-September-2012.aspx|archive-date=21 February 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Geo News Video|url=http://videos.geo.tv/VideoGallery.aspx?ID=4856|publisher=Geo News|accessdate=8 April 2012}}</ref> \nHe is currently the anchor of ''Insight'' on Business Plus, a program that focuses on successful businessmen in Pakistan.<ref>{{cite web|title=Business Plus|url=http://www.businessplustv.pk/#|publisher=Business Plus}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=My life Story|url=http://www.metacafe.com/watch/9149711/nadeem_naqvi_my_life_story_part_1/|publisher=Salman Ghouri/Businessplus/Producer|accessdate=26 September 2012}}</ref>  He has previously anchored current affairs programs on Waqt News.<ref>{{cite web|title=The Right Question 24 February 12|url=http://waqtnews.tv/episode/the-right-24-february-2012|publisher=Waqt News TV|access-date=22 April 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220120253/http://waqtnews.tv/episode/the-right-24-february-2012|archive-date=20 February 2014|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Right Question 10 March|url=http://waqtnews.tv/episode/the-right-question-10-march-2012|publisher=Waqt News|access-date=1 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127124955/http://waqtnews.tv/episode/the-right-question-10-march-2012|archive-date=27 January 2013|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Waqt News 3 March|url=http://waqtnews.tv/episode/the-right-question-03-march-2012|publisher=Waqt News|access-date=1 November 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127130331/http://waqtnews.tv/episode/the-right-question-03-march-2012|archive-date=27 January 2013|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref>   He also appears as an analyst on ''AAJ Markets'' (AAJ TV), ''Morning Shout'' (Business Plus), and ''Daily Business'' (INN-Indus News).\nNasir also narrated and hosted a documentary on [[Quaid-e-Azam]], the founder of Pakistan (in English). \nNasir has been awarded the best anchor in the business category on 22 February (7th Consumer Choice Awards).<ref>{{Citation|last = Ali Nasir|title = Ali Nasir receiving 7th Consumers Choice Award 2011|date = 2012-03-29|url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ch9V8kOix0k|accessdate = 2016-04-13}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Nasir, Ali}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Pakistani economists]]\n[[Category:Pakistani television hosts]]\n[[Category:1978 births]]\n[[Category:People from Sialkot]]\n", "text_old": "{{for|the Pakistani cricketer|Ali Nasir (cricketer)}}\n{{Use Pakistani English|date=July 2013}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2013}}\n\n\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Ali Nasir\n| image = Ali Nasir.JPG\n| caption = \n| birthname = \n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1978|10|7}}\n| birth_place = [[Sialkot, Pakistan]]\n| death_date =\n| death_place =\n| occupation = Economist<br>Entrepreneur<br>TV anchor<br>Journalist\n| years_active = 2009\u2013present\n| title =\n| family =\n| spouse =\n| children =\n| relatives =\n| salary = \n| networth =\n| credits = [[Business Plus (TV Channel)|Business Plus]]'s ''Live Wire Insight'' anchor<br> ''Morning Shout'' co-anchor<br>[[Waqt News]] ''The Right Question'' anchor <br> [[Indus TV]]'s ''Talking Business'' anchor\n<br> [[Indus Vision]]'s \"Studio 3\"<ref>{{cite web|last=Ghumman|first=Arsalan|title=PTI Official Page|url=http://www.insaf.pk/Media/Videos/tabid/62/articleType/ArticleView/articleId/15361/Studio3-Arsalan-Ghumman-on-Youth-and-comming-elections-March-12-2013.aspx|publisher=PTI|accessdate=17 March 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316075207/http